<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html> 
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="zh-cn" />
  <meta name="robots" content="all" />
  <meta name="author" content="happy.cd" />
  <meta name="Copyright" content="happy.cd Lcd, All Rights Reserved." />
  <title><%= yield(:title) %> </title>
  <meta name="keywords" content="<%= yield(:meta_keywords)%>" />
  <meta name="description" content="<%= yield(:meta_description)%>" />
    
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag  "content", "index_style" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "jquery", "jquery-ui", "jquery.sliders", "addresses", "index_script" %>

  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <!--[if lt IE 7]>
    <link href="/assets/ie_style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <![endif]-->
  <!--[if IE 6]>
    <script src="/assets/iepng.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
       EvPNG.fix('img,#logo a,.wanmh,.bcpic,.input_search_txt,.subit,.sinaweibo,.txweibo'); 
    </script>
  <![endif]-->
</head> 

<body>
<div id="header">
  <!-- jQuery handles to place the header background images -->
  <div id="headerimgs">
    <div id="headerimg1" class="headerimg"></div>
    <div id="headerimg2" class="headerimg"></div>
  </div>
  <!-- Top navigation on top of the images -->
  <div id="nav-outer">
    <div id="navigation">
      <div id="search">
        <%= yield %>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Slideshow controls -->
  <div id="headernav-outer">
    <div id="headernav">
      <div id="back" class="btn"></div>
      <div id="control" class="btn"></div>
      <div id="next" class="btn"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- jQuery handles for the text displayed on top of the images -->
  <div id="headertxt">
    <p class="caption">
      <span id="firstline"></span>
      <a href="#" id="secondline"></a>
    </p>
    <p class="pictured">
      Pictured:
      <a href="#" id="pictureduri"></a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="content">
  <p>&nbsp;</p>
  <p style="color: #cc3333; font-size: 2em; font-weight: 700; font-family: "黑体"; line-height: 20px; padding: 10px 0;">洋盘吧， 成都也可以在线订外卖了~ 你试过没？</p>
  <p style="color: #090; font-size: 2em; line-height: 20px; padding: 10px 0;">想叫外卖了？就上成都乐活， happy.cd</p>
  <p style="font-weight: 600;">1分钟订餐，半小时等待，3000家餐厅，上万道美食!</p>
  <p>乐活外卖基于地理位置, 为您呈现您所在区域的餐厅和外卖信息。 您可以直接通过网络订餐，订餐成功后，外卖会在30分钟--1个小时之内及时送达！您所需的操作只有三步："确定您所在的区域" ---> "点菜" ---> "留下电话和地址，下单！" .</p>
